config INPUT_AW86937_Y700
	tristate "Lenovo Y700 AW86937 haptics"
	depends on I2C && INPUT
	select REGMAP_I2C
	help
	  Say Y here to enable the dual AW86937 haptic ICs used by the
	  Lenovo Y700. The driver exposes standard input force-feedback
	  FF_RUMBLE devices and intentionally preserves the chip boot-time
	  boost register value.

	  To compile this driver as a module, choose M here: the module will
	  be called aw86937-y700.
